scimax.export.latex.customHeader.markdownDescription:
Custom LaTeX header (preamble) that replaces the auto-generated one. Should include `\documentclass` through all `\usepackage` commands. Example:
```latex
\documentclass[11pt]{article}
\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}
\usepackage{graphicx}
```

scimax.export.latex.defaultPreamble.markdownDescription:
Default LaTeX preamble (packages and commands) added after `\documentclass`. Can be extended by `#+LATEX_HEADER:` lines in the document. Example:
```latex
\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}
\usepackage{graphicx}
\usepackage{amsmath}
```
